{"tid":1755252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區議員應立即籌備罷工及抗爭基金","createTime":"2019-11-25T13:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T13:57:10.000Z","uid":135890,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0b2c36fbb6b78f5209251161d4389495fad670ac","tid":1755252,"uid":135890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:27:45.000Z","msg":"由612至今，各位手足為咗令各位大人有藉口罷工已經付上不少代價，有手足被親共分子襲擊，有手足受實彈槍擊。<br />\n<br />\n各位區議員，你們每一席、每一票也是用血用汗用淚造就而成，現時的形勢是每個香港人把希望寄托於你們，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切勿得到議席而尸位素餐，立即準備運用區議會資源籌備罷工及抗爭基金！</span></strong>讓有需要的同行手兄得到協助<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724fe977d904a693d2441d661f85a541973853a2","tid":1755252,"uid":135890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:28:13.000Z","msg":"開多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5909e8063fe89e7db2e4124def3b2535676ecf9","tid":1755252,"uid":135890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:28:52.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed846211f995a24165830eb5a1adf04b891ce85","tid":1755252,"uid":135890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:29:38.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"de4febb00277608ea3f584bcf323a20b5e7812b8","tid":1755252,"uid":135890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:30:06.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"f74501d809a8356ca09333466508d50b3cae6fde","tid":1755252,"uid":6953,"like":0,"